		<div id="comment_body_64517495"><p>"type 2 diabetes and gestational diabetes can be totally reversed with a Nutritarian diet."</p><p>Absolute nonsense except very, very early on (long before insulin dependence).  And you have to lose a lot of weight very fast.  Even then usually all it does is delay later onset for a time.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64517495">
