		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64517567"><p>I get that you want to believe literally everything that the CCP says, from GDP to pandemic fatalities, but even if we took them at their word (just...why? I don't get people like you...) this remains a one-off. Science just doesn't work that way. It needs to be repeatable, and until it is, it's just tabloid material. So Betterage remains for the time being.</p></div>
