	<div id="comment_top_64517517" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64517517" name="comment_link_64517517" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23342743&amp;cid=64517517" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64517517)" >Didn't we find one already?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64517517" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64517517); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Samare">Samare</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Samare">( 2779329 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64517517">		
		on Sunday June 02, 2024 @10:53AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23342743&amp;cid=64517517">#64517517</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64517517"><p>"A larger study analyzed 232 patients with diabetes who were placed on a plant-based diet as part of a residential dietary intervention program. More than 90% of patients were able to decrease or discontinue their diabetes medications in just 7 days while improving or maintaining control of their diabetes. A review of 14 randomized diet trials concluded that the best results occurred with plant-based diets."<br><a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5638636/" title="nih.gov">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/p...</a> [nih.gov] (Lifestyle Medicine: A Brief Review of Its Dramatic Impact on Health and Survival)</p></div>
	</div>

